short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Clicking on the extension button sorts alphabetically the participant data attributes on an interaction detail page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
In Genesys Cloud, when looking at an interaction details, the participant data attributes are not alphabetically sorted. This simple extension sorts the participant data attributes in an alphabetical order when clicking on the extension button

Disclaimer: this not an official Genesys product and is not supported by Genesys.
